    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Exceptional mint-condition example that presents like a car that has been carefully preserved or comprehensively sorted to a very high standard. The paint, trim, glass, and interior should all show beautifully, with excellent fit, finish, and detail throughout, and it appears ready to enjoy immediately. This is not just a usable driver but a standout car for a buyer who wants one of the best-kept examples available.",
