      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Clean, honest good-condition car that presents well overall and should make a strong impression without pretending to be perfect. The body and paint show nicely with the expected minor cosmetic wear and age-related imperfections you\u2019d anticipate on a used vehicle, and the interior appears well-kept and comfortable with normal signs of use. It looks like a car that has been maintained and enjoyed rather than neglected, and a buyer should expect a solid, attractive example that is ready to use right away while still showing some typical wear if you look closely.",
      "price": 33900.0,
