      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Great budget-friendly opportunity for a buyer who wants dependable basic transportation at an accessible price. This vehicle shows its age and is best suited for someone comfortable with cosmetic wear and ongoing maintenance, but it offers strong value as an inexpensive daily driver, backup vehicle, or project. Straightforward, affordable, and priced to move.",
